Articles.Content:
I'm working on a 1.1.3 RSS/RO Block 3+ CSM style spacecraft. I have an orbital module below the CSM that I dock to and extract. My problem is that when I perform the TD&E I can not transfer crew to the OM. However when I set it up in the VAB and launch it with clamps supporting it, I can transfer to the OM. I am using APAS 89-95 Docking ports. Where should I be looking for the problem?

 

CSM/OM only
